title: 👶 That's One BALD Baby! (Cocomelon) #shorts
description:
There’s absolutely NO way that JJ from Cocomelon is a baby. Based on the way he walks, talks, sleeps, and poops he HAS to be at least 3 years old. So, why then, does he not have hair when every other toddler around his age has it?
